"use strict";(self.webpackChunkcontrolz_docs=self.webpackChunkcontrolz_docs||[]).push([[2623],{1714:e=>{e.exports=JSON.parse('{"archive":{"blogPosts":[{"id":"closed-test-release-2025-1-5","metadata":{"permalink":"/Controlz-Docs/cz/blog/closed-test-release-2025-1-5","source":"@site/i18n/cz/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2025-05-17-post.md","title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed Controlz 2025.1.5","description":"Popis","date":"2025-05-17T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Dev","permalink":"/Controlz-Docs/cz/blog/tags/dev","description":"Development news"},{"inline":false,"label":"Test","permalink":"/Controlz-Docs/cz/blog/tags/test","description":"Testing news"}],"readingTime":0.46,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Maxim","title":"Controlz developer","url":"https://github.com/llOzzeell","page":{"permalink":"/Controlz-Docs/cz/blog/authors/maxim"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/llOzzeell"},"imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/45766241?v=4","key":"maxim"}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"closed-test-release-2025-1-5","title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed Controlz 2025.1.5","authors":["maxim"],"tags":["dev","test"]},"unlisted":false,"nextItem":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed Controlz 2025.1.4","permalink":"/Controlz-Docs/cz/blog/closed-test-release-2025-1-4"}},"content":"### Popis\\n\\nTato aktualizace zlep\u0161uje pr\xe1ci s bloky, zvy\u0161uje v\xfdkon a zaji\u0161\u0165uje spr\xe1vnou funk\u010dnost na nov\u011bj\u0161\xedch verz\xedch Androidu.\\n\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\n---\\n\\n### Zm\u011bny\\n\\n- **Opraven\xe1 chyba p\u0159i skenov\xe1n\xed hub\u016f na Androidu 12+** \u2013 nyn\xed se vy\u017eaduje opr\xe1vn\u011bn\xed k p\u0159esn\xe9 poloze.\\n- **P\u0159id\xe1na mo\u017enost skr\xfdt/zobrazit paletu blok\u016f** kliknut\xedm na pr\xe1v\u011b vybranou kolekci blok\u016f.\\n- **P\u0159id\xe1na rukoje\u0165 pro zm\u011bnu velikosti** palety blok\u016f pro **ru\u010dn\xed \xfapravu velikosti**.\\n- **Opraven\xe9 vysok\xe9 zat\xed\u017een\xed CPU**, kdy\u017e byl profil na\u010dten, ale program nebyl spu\u0161t\u011bn.\\n- **Vylep\u0161en\xfd editor bloku \u201eSeznam \u0159et\u011bzc\u016f\u201c**, aby se zabr\xe1nilo o\u0159ez\xe1v\xe1n\xed obsahu. Polo\u017eky jsou nyn\xed rozd\u011bleny do sloupc\u016f pro lep\u0161\xed p\u0159ehlednost u dlouh\xfdch seznam\u016f."},{"id":"closed-test-release-2025-1-4","metadata":{"permalink":"/Controlz-Docs/cz/blog/closed-test-release-2025-1-4","source":"@site/i18n/cz/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2025-05-10-post.md","title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed Controlz 2025.1.4","description":"Popis","date":"2025-05-10T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Dev","permalink":"/Controlz-Docs/cz/blog/tags/dev","description":"Development news"},{"inline":false,"label":"Test","permalink":"/Controlz-Docs/cz/blog/tags/test","description":"Testing news"}],"readingTime":0.77,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Maxim","title":"Controlz developer","url":"https://github.com/llOzzeell","page":{"permalink":"/Controlz-Docs/cz/blog/authors/maxim"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/llOzzeell"},"imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/45766241?v=4","key":"maxim"}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"closed-test-release-2025-1-4","title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed Controlz 2025.1.4","authors":["maxim"],"tags":["dev","test"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed Controlz 2025.1.5","permalink":"/Controlz-Docs/cz/blog/closed-test-release-2025-1-5"},"nextItem":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed Controlz 2025.1.2 \u2013 2025.1.3","permalink":"/Controlz-Docs/cz/blog/closed-test-release-2025-1-2-3"}},"content":"### Popis\\n\\nTato aktualizace zlep\u0161uje podporu pro tablety, p\u0159id\xe1v\xe1 u\u017eite\u010dn\xe9 testovac\xed str\xe1nky a opravuje n\u011bkolik probl\xe9m\u016f s kompatibilitou a v\xfdkonem.\\n\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\n---\\n\\n### Zm\u011bny\\n\\n- **P\u0159id\xe1no rozvr\u017een\xed pro tablety** pro lep\u0161\xed vyu\u017eit\xed v\u011bt\u0161\xedch obrazovek.\\n- **Opraven\xe1 chyba, kdy se blok \u201etla\u010d\xedtko na hubu stisknuto\u201c** zobrazoval i pro huby, kter\xe9 tuto akci nepodporuj\xed. Tak\xe9 opraveny **bloky pro barevn\xfd senzor** u nepodporovan\xfdch hub\u016f (nap\u0159. BuWizz).\\n- **Opraven\xe1 chyba, kdy blok \u201eb\u011bh motoru\u201c** neovliv\u0148oval motory bez enkod\xe9r\u016f kv\u016fli chyb\u011bj\xedc\xedm alternativn\xedm p\u0159\xedkaz\u016fm.\\n- **P\u0159id\xe1na str\xe1nka pro testov\xe1n\xed tla\u010d\xedtek gamepadu.**\\n- **P\u0159id\xe1na str\xe1nka pro testov\xe1n\xed hubu** s p\u0159ehledem informac\xed, p\u0159ipojen\xfdch za\u0159\xedzen\xed na portech a stavem ot\u0159es\u016f port\u016f.\\n- **Opraven\xfd nespr\xe1vn\xfd v\xfdklad dat z akcelerometru** pro BuWizz 2 a 3, kter\xfd zp\u016fsoboval chybn\xe9 orienta\u010dn\xed \xfadaje.\\n- **Opraven\xe9 \xfaniky pam\u011bti RAM**, kter\xe9 vedly k ukon\u010den\xed aplikace na n\u011bkter\xfdch za\u0159\xedzen\xedch kv\u016fli vysok\xe9 spot\u0159eb\u011b pam\u011bti.\\n- **Opraven\xe9 chyby p\u0159i na\u010d\xedt\xe1n\xed profil\u016f**, kter\xe9 d\u0159\xedve zp\u016fsobovaly p\xe1dy aplikace v ur\u010dit\xfdch sc\xe9n\xe1\u0159\xedch.\\n- **Opraven\xe1 chyba na Androidu**, kdy uvoln\u011bn\xed p\xe1\u010dek gamepadu nenastavilo hodnoty os zp\u011bt na nulu."},{"id":"closed-test-release-2025-1-2-3","metadata":{"permalink":"/Controlz-Docs/cz/blog/closed-test-release-2025-1-2-3","source":"@site/i18n/cz/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2025-04-19-post.md","title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed Controlz 2025.1.2 \u2013 2025.1.3","description":"Popis","date":"2025-04-19T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Dev","permalink":"/Controlz-Docs/cz/blog/tags/dev","description":"Development news"},{"inline":false,"label":"Test","permalink":"/Controlz-Docs/cz/blog/tags/test","description":"Testing news"}],"readingTime":0.4,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Maxim","title":"Controlz developer","url":"https://github.com/llOzzeell","page":{"permalink":"/Controlz-Docs/cz/blog/authors/maxim"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/llOzzeell"},"imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/45766241?v=4","key":"maxim"}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"closed-test-release-2025-1-2-3","title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed Controlz 2025.1.2 \u2013 2025.1.3","authors":["maxim"],"tags":["dev","test"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed Controlz 2025.1.4","permalink":"/Controlz-Docs/cz/blog/closed-test-release-2025-1-4"},"nextItem":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed Controlz 2025.1.1","permalink":"/Controlz-Docs/cz/blog/closed-test-release-2025-1-1"}},"content":"### Popis\\n\\nTato aktualizace p\u0159in\xe1\u0161\xed nov\xe9 mo\u017enosti p\u0159izp\u016fsoben\xed joysticku, vylep\u0161en\xed u\u017eivatelsk\xe9ho rozhran\xed a d\u016fle\u017eit\xe9 opravy stability.\\n\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\n---\\n\\n### Zm\u011bny\\n\\n- **Opraven\xe1 chyba ve v\xfdb\u011bru kolekce blok\u016f v palet\u011b**: v\xfdb\u011br kolekce, posun na jinou a n\xe1vrat zp\u011bt nem\u011bl \u017e\xe1dn\xfd efekt.\\n- **Opraven p\xe1d aplikace p\u0159i na\u010d\xedt\xe1n\xed n\xe1ro\u010dn\xfdch profil\u016f** s velk\xfdm mno\u017estv\xedm blok\u016f.\\n- **P\u0159id\xe1na vlastnost \u201eTyp os\u201c** do nastaven\xed joysticku pro podporu **re\u017eimu s jednou osou** (X, Y, XY).\\n- **P\u0159id\xe1no barevn\xe9 odli\u0161en\xed** pro volantov\xe9 ovlada\u010de (\u201eGMZ\u201c, \u201eNo Mercy\u201c).\\n- **P\u0159id\xe1ny bloky \u201eje stisknuto\u201c** pro volanty a ped\xe1ly."},{"id":"closed-test-release-2025-1-1","metadata":{"permalink":"/Controlz-Docs/cz/blog/closed-test-release-2025-1-1","source":"@site/i18n/cz/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2025-04-14-post.md","title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed Controlz 2025.1.1","description":"Popis","date":"2025-04-14T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Dev","permalink":"/Controlz-Docs/cz/blog/tags/dev","description":"Development news"},{"inline":false,"label":"Test","permalink":"/Controlz-Docs/cz/blog/tags/test","description":"Testing news"}],"readingTime":0.44,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Maxim","title":"Controlz developer","url":"https://github.com/llOzzeell","page":{"permalink":"/Controlz-Docs/cz/blog/authors/maxim"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/llOzzeell"},"imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/45766241?v=4","key":"maxim"}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"closed-test-release-2025-1-1","title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed Controlz 2025.1.1","authors":["maxim"],"tags":["dev","test"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed Controlz 2025.1.2 \u2013 2025.1.3","permalink":"/Controlz-Docs/cz/blog/closed-test-release-2025-1-2-3"},"nextItem":{"title":"Controlz 2025.1.0","permalink":"/Controlz-Docs/cz/blog/closed-test-begin"}},"content":"### Popis\\n\\nTato aktualizace obsahuje n\u011bkolik d\u016fle\u017eit\xfdch oprav chyb, kter\xe9 zlep\u0161uj\xed v\xfdkon, sni\u017euj\xed spot\u0159ebu baterie a zlep\u0161uj\xed chov\xe1n\xed blok\u016f v programovac\xedm prost\u0159ed\xed.\\n\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\n---\\n\\n### Zm\u011bny\\n\\n- **Opraven\xe1 chyba zp\u016fsobuj\xedc\xed vysok\xe9 vyu\u017eit\xed CPU, vyb\xedjen\xed baterie a n\xedzk\xfd v\xfdkon.**\\n- **Opraven\xe1 chyba, kdy bloky pro gamepad** (nap\u0159. \u201eje tla\u010d\xedtko stisknuto\u201c, \u201eje stisknuto tla\u010d\xedtko D-PAD\u201c) **nebylo mo\u017en\xe9 p\u0159ipojit k jin\xfdm blok\u016fm.**\\n- **Opraven probl\xe9m v bloku ud\xe1losti p\u0159ep\xedna\u010de krok\u016f**, kter\xfd nespr\xe1vn\u011b zpracov\xe1val dotykov\xe9 ud\xe1losti a po\u010d\xedt\xe1n\xed krok\u016f.\\n- **Opraven\xe1 chyba v bloku seznamu \u201epolo\u017eka ze\u201c**, kde nebylo mo\u017en\xe9 p\u0159ipojit v\xedce ne\u017e jeden blok jako index argumentu."},{"id":"closed-test-begin","metadata":{"permalink":"/Controlz-Docs/cz/blog/closed-test-begin","source":"@site/i18n/cz/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2025-04-04-post.md","title":"Controlz 2025.1.0","description":"\ud83d\ude80 Uzav\u0159en\xe1 beta verze Controlz 2025.1.0 pr\xe1v\u011b za\u010dala!","date":"2025-04-04T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Dev","permalink":"/Controlz-Docs/cz/blog/tags/dev","description":"Development news"},{"inline":false,"label":"Test","permalink":"/Controlz-Docs/cz/blog/tags/test","description":"Testing news"}],"readingTime":0.28,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Maxim","title":"Controlz developer","url":"https://github.com/llOzzeell","page":{"permalink":"/Controlz-Docs/cz/blog/authors/maxim"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/llOzzeell"},"imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/45766241?v=4","key":"maxim"}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"closed-test-begin","title":"Controlz 2025.1.0","authors":["maxim"],"tags":["dev","test"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Vyd\xe1n\xed Controlz 2025.1.1","permalink":"/Controlz-Docs/cz/blog/closed-test-release-2025-1-1"}},"content":"## \ud83d\ude80 Uzav\u0159en\xe1 beta verze Controlz 2025.1.0 pr\xe1v\u011b za\u010dala!\\n\\nS radost\xed oznamujeme, \u017ee uzav\u0159en\xe9 beta testov\xe1n\xed Controlz 2025 je nyn\xed spu\u0161t\u011bno! Vybran\xed u\u017eivatel\xe9 mohou nyn\xed prozkoumat nov\xe9 funkce, poskytnout zp\u011btnou vazbu a pomoci formovat budoucnost aplikace Controlz.\\n\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\n\\nPokud jste obdr\u017eeli pozv\xe1nku, zkontrolujte si sv\u016fj e-mail pro p\u0159\xedstupov\xe9 \xfadaje.  \\nD\u011bkujeme, \u017ee jste sou\u010d\xe1st\xed t\xe9to d\u016fle\u017eit\xe9 f\xe1ze!"}]}}')}}]);